XWiki should be set with very large memory settings, high cache:
* Set -Xmx and -Xms to half the memory of the machine (16g for 32g RAM) * Set cache to 5000 in xwiki.cfg (instead of 500)
Heavy processes should be disabled:
* Deactivate notifications in xwiki.properties (optional) * Deactivate notifications on your own profile ("never" for automatic page watching, disable page notifications) * Clean Notifications: run [[CleanNotificationsPrefs>>Confluence.Tools.CleanNotificationsPrefs||target='_blank']] (optional) * Deactivate SOLR and Notifications listeners ** from XWiki.ListenerAdmin page on main wiki : #set ($listenerAdminDoc = $xwiki.getDocument('XWiki.ListenerAdmin')) #set ($solrIndexURL = $listenerAdminDoc.getURL('view', '#|t=listeners&listenerClass=SolrIndexEventListener')) #set ($automaticWatchURL = $listenerAdminDoc.getURL('view', '#|t=listeners&listenerClass=AutomaticWatchModeListener')) #set ($liveNotificationURL = $listenerAdminDoc.getURL('view', '#|t=listeners&listenerClass=LiveNotificationEmailListener')) *** [[SolrIndexEventListener>>path:$solrIndexURL||target='_blank']] (optional, as this would disable SOLR indexing for the whole farm) ## The DocumentMovedListener is available from XWiki 11.3. #if ($services.extension.core.getCoreExtension('org.xwiki.platform:xwiki-platform-model').id.version.compareTo('11.3') >= 0) #set ($documentMovedURL = $listenerAdminDoc.getURL('view', '#|t=listeners&listenerClass=DocumentMovedListener')) *** [[DocumentMovedListener>>path:$documentMovedURL||target='_blank']] (important for large spaces) #end *** [[AutomaticWatchModeListener>>path:$automaticWatchURL||target='_blank']] (important for large spaces) *** [[LiveNotificationEmailListener>>path:$liveNotificationURL||target='_blank']] (important for large spaces) {{/velocity}}
